*Vidjeli* smo kako se sunce spustilo na horizont. (We saw how the sun set on the horizon.)

Čuli smo njihove nade kad su *vidjeli* da imaju pravo. (We heard their hopes when they saw that they were right.)

*Vidjeli* smo da je ona bila tužna. (We saw that she was sad.)

Oni su već *vidjeli* tu sliku. (They had already seen that picture.)

Kad je *vidjela* da je zaboravila ključeve, bila je zabrinuta. (When she saw that she had forgotten the keys, she was worried.)